{"type":"message","id":"0ab530aa","parentId":"f5e4e8c2","timestamp":"2026-03-24T17:05:52.743Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It seems the pulse script already committed. Let me check the status.","thinkingSignature":"355013911373883c29f322301e9461a946caaf7dfae9524583ace3b985b8e10b"},{"type":"text","text":"**Sandbox Pulse Summary (2026-03-24 13:05)**\n\n✅ **Status:** Clean — nothing to commit\n\n📊 **Key Findings from CFI Compression Research:**\n- Binary threshold strategies (A/B) identified frequency alone isn't enough — need **CFI dimension** (Conditional Format Independence)\n- **Strategy C** proposed: hybrid scoring formula `score(T) = CFI(T) × min(1, freq(T)/120)`\n  - Rewards both format consistency (CFI) AND frequency\n  - Constant-format tokens get max score (1.0)\n  - Rare tokens get proportionally reduced credit\n\n🔬 **Next Step for Future Pulse:** Implement `experiments/strategy_c_hybrid_scoring.py` to test the hybrid formula against the pulse corpus\n\n📁 **Commit:** `8ff6ad6` — 5 files changed, +297/-53 lines (includes the synthesis doc and mutation proposal)"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2017,"output":209,"cacheRead":12137,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14363,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774371947192}}
